### Get Integration Status
# Returns the status and config of all opt-in integrations (SMTP, OpenTelemetry, OpenPanel).
# Requires a valid Bearer JWT (admin role) in Authorization header.
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/integrations
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

###

### Send Test Email
# Sends a test email to the authenticated admin's email address.
# Requires SMTP to be enabled (SMTP_HOST env var must be set).
# Requires a valid Bearer JWT (admin role) in Authorization header.
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/integrations/mail/test
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}
